none: Korean linguist Ku Cha-gyun (1912-1964) researched the hansi of the middle class in Chosŏn dynasty. It is an edited version of Ku's graduation thesis for Kyŏngsŏng Cheguk Taehakkyo (now Seoul National University) in 1936.
